*Interesantno* je što nikad ne znaš šta će se desiti u budućnosti. (It is interesting that you never know what will happen in the future.)

Svi su se složili da je ovo *interesantno* otkriće. (Everyone agreed that this is an interesting discovery.)

Ona je smatrala da je to *interesantno*. (She thought it was interesting.)

*Interesantno* je da se stvari u životu menjaju brzo. (It is interesting that things in life change quickly.)

Njeno ponašanje bilo je *interesantno*. (Her behavior was interesting.)